---
title: Smart Ginger-Hoisin Tilapia  with Super Crunch Salad and Peanut-Lime Dressing
description: Known as the Asian BBQ sauce, hoisin sauce pulls double duty in this recipe to bring subtle sweetness to both sauteed tilapia and peanut-lime dressing! This salad is equal parts exciting and delicious!

